The error I get with --debug:

{code}
Debug: Prefetching pacman resources for package
Debug: Executing '/usr/bin/pacman -Q'
Debug: Executing '/usr/bin/pacman -Sgg'
Debug: Executing '/usr/bin/pacman -Q'
Debug: Executing '/usr/bin/pacman -Sgg unifi'
